Bellevue.KUOW-FM: KUOW-FM 94.9 is a National Public Radio member station in Seattle, Washington. It is the larger of the two full-fledged NPR member stations in the Seattle/Tacoma media market, Tacoma-based KNKX is the other. It is a service of the University of Washington, but is operated by KUOW Puget Sound Public Radio, a nonprofit community organization.
